time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: The solution iterates through the operations in reverse order, tracking the length of the string and the shift in characters. It adjusts k accordingly to find the kth character after all operations, utilizing the properties of the given operations to efficiently compute the result.
